metadata.name: Ultimate Key  -  #1/1
metadata.description:
The Ultimate Key is a 1/1 key for the collector of my rarest artwork from my genesis collection “Follow Your Daydreams - 35 1/1s captured on film” which is the only artwork shot on Super 8 film in the collection, essentially making it a 1/1 of a 1/1. I used metadata to build rarities into each 1/1 image based on what kind of film I used…This is one use case for those rarities built into my genesis collection. (You hold the 1/1, you get access to another 1/1).

"Keys" will grant you access to the "I Lost My Keys" collection
